                <td style="padding: 15px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                  <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block;">
                    🟢 Active
                  </span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 15px 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #475569; font-size: 15px;">
                  📅 Registered On
                </td>
                <td style="padding: 15px 10px; color: #1e293b; font-size: 15px;">
                  ${new Date(created_at || Date.now()).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>

          <!-- What you can do -->
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 5px solid #10b981;">
            <h3 style="color: #166534; margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;">
              ✨ What You Can Do Now
            </h3>
            <ul style="margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 20px; color: #14532d; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2;">
              <li><strong>Manage bookings</strong> through your dashboard</li>
              <li><strong>Update room availability</strong> in real-time</li>
              <li><strong>Set your own prices</strong> - no hidden commissions</li>
              <li><strong>Add photos and descriptions</strong> to showcase your hotel</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Support section -->
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef9c3 0%, #fef08a 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 5px solid #eab308;">
            <h3 style="color: #854d0e; margin: 0 0 15px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;">
              💡 Need Help?
            </h3>
            <p style="color: #713f12; margin: 0 0 15px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8;">
