            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
              <a href="mailto:support@naity.net" style="display: inline-block; background: #1a56db; color: white; padding: 14px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.3);">
                📧 Contact us: support@naity.net
              </a>
            </div>
            <p style="color: #713f12; margin: 15px 0 0; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
              📍 Syria - Damascus
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Closing message -->
          <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px;">
            <p style="color: #0369a1; margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">
              Thank you for trusting Naity! 🤝
            </p>
            <p style="color: #475569; margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 15px;">
              We look forward to a successful partnership
            </p>
          </div>
